   <div id="about">
    <h3>The Eastgrove Difference</h3>
     <p>We make affordable, high quality guitars.  Our bodies and necks are crafted and assembled in Asia, just like every other guitar that sells for $500.  What makes us unique is that we install high quality electronics, perform a fret dress and level, and include a professional setup all in our U.S.A. facility></p><br>
   </div>
   <div id="electronics">
    <h4>Our Pickups</h4>
     <p>We install high-quality, hand wound pickups in every one of our guitars.  Pete Ostlund is world-renowned for the quality of his boutique pickups.  You can rest assured that you are getting the finest pickups on the market- built and installed in the U.S.A.</p>
     <iframe id="video" width="560" height="315"src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yCQN6A_JyXo" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
