   <div id="setup">
    <h5>The Setup</h5>
     <p>Our guitar technicians have over 100 years of combined experience.  We work through every guitar with meticulous attention to detail.  We adjust the trust rod to provide the perfect neck angle.  We set the string height and intonation.  We go the extra mile in providing a fret level and dress, making our guitars the best playing, affordable guitars on the market.</p>
